<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<!-- Developer ID distribution outside the App Store: no provisioning profile and no team-specific
     entitlements (keychain-access-groups / application-identifier / team-identifier removed with the
     Palmier identity). Hardened Runtime is applied at codesign time via `--options runtime`. Add a
     specific com.apple.security.cs.* entitlement here only if a notarized launch turns out to need it. -->
<dict/>
</plist>
